  &lt;span class=&#34;token keyword&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; choice&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;token comment&#34;&gt;// [rsp+4h] [rbp-Ch]&lt;/span&gt;
